1. Juče sam *pustila* pesmu koju volim. (Yesterday I played the song I love.)
2. Molim te, *pusti* me da odem kući. (Please, let me go home.)
3. Kada sam došla u sobu, primetila sam da sam *pustila* svetlo. (When I entered the room, I noticed that I left the light on.)
4. Nisam mogla da verujem da sam mu *pustila* da mi ukrade novac. (I couldn't believe that I allowed him to steal my money.)
5. Uvek *puštam* da me srce vodi. (I always let my heart lead me.)
6. *Pustite* me da završim posao do kraja dana. (Let me finish the work by the end of the day.)
7. Bila sam toliko ljuta da sam *pustila* suzu. (I was so angry that I shed a tear.)
8. Kada sam otišla na odmor, *pustila* sam svoje brige iza sebe. (When I went on vacation, I left my worries behind.)
9. Nisam mogla da verujem da sam *pustila* priliku da budem sa njim. (I couldn't believe that I missed the chance to be with him.)
10. Možete li mi *pustiti* tu knjigu da je pozajmim? (Can you lend me that book?)